 PyUrlShortener is a application for Url shortening using python and taking information from my php website http://pycutter.uphero.com

   
   //---------------//  
  //  INSTALLATION //
 //-------------- //

To install PyUrlShortener enter the following command in the directory where pycutter is extracted:

"$ sudo python setup.py install"

that's it PyUrlShortener is installed on your linux machine

for executing the PyUrlShortener
enter
 $ pycutter "http://URL"
 In the next line your shorten url is displayed



